# UXDS Story Loop Routing

Before implementing or merging UX Design Studio work:

1. Read and follow `AGENTS.md`, including `Authorized Autonomous Epic Runs` when a run manifest is active.
2. Discover the active authorized manifest under `.agents/runs/` (exactly one `active: true` run).
3. Load the canonical story-loop skill at `.agents/skills/uxds-story-loop/SKILL.md`.
4. Invoke the independent read-only verifier contract at `.agents/verifiers/uxds-story-verifier.md` before commit and merge.
5. Preserve WIP limit 1, signed commits, merge commits, retained feature branches, and no direct pushes to `staging` or `main`.
6. Prohibit autonomy outside an authorized run manifest. Do not start another epic after the authorized epic completes.
7. Keep canonical rules in `.agents/**`; do not duplicate or weaken them here.
